SchemaItem.Name: 00010_View_BusinessProcessRequest_RelatedProcessList
SchemaItem.M01:
alter view BusinessProcessRequest_RelatedProcessList as select newid() as Id, * from ( select refBusinessProcessRequestId, refOldBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId as refBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId, refBusinessProcessRequestProcessChangeTypeId, cast(RequestedChangeDescription as nvarchar(1000)) RequestedChangeDescription from BusinessProcessRequestProcess where refOldBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId is not null
union
select refBusinessProcessRequestId, refNewBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId as refBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId, refBusinessProcessRequestProcessChangeTypeId, cast(RequestedChangeDescription as nvarchar(1000)) RequestedChangeDescription from BusinessProcessRequestProcess where refNewBusinessProcessDefinitionVersionId is not null ) as List

SchemaItem.Name: BusinessProcessDefinition_AssignReferenceCode
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <xsl:apply-templates select="BusinessProcessDefinition"/> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="BusinessProcessDefinition"> <ROOT> <xsl:variable name="CounterCode" select="AS:LookupValue('8fb5c9d2-d256-4c26-b77d-ae623caf82be', @refBusinessProcessTypeId)"/>
<xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="ReferenceCode"><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateSerial($CounterCode)"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </ROOT> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
